1
00:00:00,499 --> 00:00:05,023
♪A little bit sorry for my love for you♪

2
00:00:05,023 --> 00:00:10,527
♪Sorry, I was a little late♪

3
00:00:10,527 --> 00:00:16,955
♪I really want the unconscious longing
to appear faster♪

4
00:00:16,955 --> 00:00:21,435
♪Can I get closer
and hear you say "I do" once more♪

5
00:00:21,435 --> 00:00:25,883
♪Holding hands, the scenery
in midsummer is a new journey♪

6
00:00:25,883 --> 00:00:30,794
♪The chapters of a fairy tale
are performed one after another♪

7
00:00:30,794 --> 00:00:34,843
♪The promised moment
will definitely not be forgotten♪

8
00:00:34,843 --> 00:00:39,378
♪Can I get closer and listen to
the frequency of your heartbeat♪

9
00:00:39,378 --> 00:00:43,675
♪Start the countdown 4321,
a new scenery♪

10
00:00:43,675 --> 00:00:48,440
♪I want to see all the scenes about you♪

11
00:00:48,440 --> 00:00:51,931
♪No need to miss you anymore♪

12
00:00:51,931 --> 00:00:55,611
♪Right by your side♪

13
00:00:57,257 --> 00:01:00,635
=Jin Secretary=

14
00:01:00,635 --> 00:01:03,104
=Episode 14=

15
00:01:04,766 --> 00:01:05,632
Be quiet.

16
00:01:07,133 --> 00:01:08,699
I am her elder sister,

17
00:01:08,699 --> 00:01:09,899
Jin Xi'er.

18
00:01:13,133 --> 00:01:16,736
I am Miss Jin's sister, Jin Xi'er.

19
00:01:18,633 --> 00:01:19,999
I'll only say this once.

20
00:01:20,200 --> 00:01:22,366
Tomorrow morning,
I'll issue a statement.

21
00:01:23,200 --> 00:01:25,066
Please stop bothering my mother.

22
00:01:25,266 --> 00:01:26,866
Get out of the hospital now.

23
00:01:28,600 --> 00:01:31,500
Can you explain what's going on?

24
00:01:43,900 --> 00:01:45,066
Be quiet.

25
00:01:51,966 --> 00:01:53,376
This is a hospital.

26
00:01:54,466 --> 00:01:56,433
I've sent lawyer's letters
to your newspapers.

27
00:01:57,966 --> 00:01:59,936
Please delete today's materials.

28
00:02:00,366 --> 00:02:02,333
And don't come here to bother them.

29
00:02:04,633 --> 00:02:06,733
You think you can do whatever you want?

30
00:02:10,400 --> 00:02:12,066
A lawyer's letter?

31
00:02:12,066 --> 00:02:13,399
We received it too.

32
00:02:13,500 --> 00:02:15,900
Stop invading other's privacy.

33
00:02:17,266 --> 00:02:18,766
- Let's go.
- Let's go.

34
00:02:31,500 --> 00:02:32,533
Thank you.

35
00:02:33,533 --> 00:02:34,933
Are you alright?

36
00:02:35,800 --> 00:02:36,633
Yes.

37
00:02:38,133 --> 00:02:39,599
I came immediately
after I heard the news.

38
00:02:40,266 --> 00:02:41,033
I'll visit your mom.

39
00:02:41,100 --> 00:02:42,466
No need. My mom is resting.

40
00:02:43,872 --> 00:02:44,766
Alright.

41
00:02:45,766 --> 00:02:47,133
Hope she will get well soon.

42
00:02:48,466 --> 00:02:52,933
Thank you. The doctor said my mom
was just scared. Nothing serious.

43
00:02:55,500 --> 00:02:58,933
Miss Jin, I want you to do me a favor.

44
00:03:00,366 --> 00:03:02,799
I hope you can be my secretary.

45
00:03:04,608 --> 00:03:06,266
You are a capable person.

46
00:03:06,400 --> 00:03:08,033
I don't want to lose a talent.

47
00:03:08,166 --> 00:03:10,533
I can double your current salary.

48
00:03:18,733 --> 00:03:20,233
I'm offering a job to you,

49
00:03:20,400 --> 00:03:21,533
not your sister.

50
00:03:24,366 --> 00:03:25,856
You knew about it?

51
00:03:27,366 --> 00:03:29,440
I knew you have a twin sister.

52
00:03:31,968 --> 00:03:34,133
So, will you accept my offer, Jin Xi'er?

53
00:03:35,872 --> 00:03:38,966
There's a lot going on right now.
Let me think about it.

54
00:03:39,800 --> 00:03:40,666
Thank you.

55
00:03:40,733 --> 00:03:42,166
As you know,

56
00:03:42,733 --> 00:03:44,864
Mr. Lan's family business is declining.

57
00:03:45,366 --> 00:03:46,466
It's seriously ill.

58
00:03:46,466 --> 00:03:47,066
No.

59
00:03:47,166 --> 00:03:49,966
I think Mr. Lan can be a good leader.

60
00:03:53,466 --> 00:03:56,399
He is lucky
to have a secretary like you.

61
00:04:00,333 --> 00:04:02,466
Do you know what he is
going to do tomorrow?

62
00:04:04,400 --> 00:04:05,466
What will you do?

63
00:04:06,933 --> 00:04:08,966
I haven't thought about that.

64
00:04:09,166 --> 00:04:12,066
I'll resolve my issue first
and take care of my mom.

65
00:04:12,666 --> 00:04:13,566
Fine.

66
00:04:14,733 --> 00:04:17,399
I'll leave these flowers for you.

67
00:04:19,733 --> 00:04:21,866
I won't disturb your mom's rest today.

68
00:04:23,500 --> 00:04:24,366
See you.

69
00:04:37,248 --> 00:04:39,743
(Inpatient Department)

70
00:05:02,500 --> 00:05:03,433
I'm sorry.

71
00:05:04,366 --> 00:05:05,999
I will handle it.

72
00:05:11,433 --> 00:05:13,000
Xi'en, do you like Lan Chen?

73
00:05:14,528 --> 00:05:18,233
♪You treated me too well♪

74
00:05:18,233 --> 00:05:20,928
Why do you always make decisions
on your own?

75
00:05:22,266 --> 00:05:25,199
You went to work for me
and threatened Mei Xiangfa and others.

76
00:05:25,266 --> 00:05:29,066
You do whatever you want,
but you never think of me and our mom.

77
00:05:29,866 --> 00:05:31,633
Why did I do this?

78
00:05:31,733 --> 00:05:35,433
Should I do nothing
as you're bullied at the company?

79
00:05:40,500 --> 00:05:43,333
Since you came back,
you've caused so much trouble.

80
00:05:44,400 --> 00:05:46,633
Ling Feng, Gu Qianqian,

81
00:05:47,166 --> 00:05:49,699
and those reporters. What will be next?

82
00:05:50,000 --> 00:05:53,600
You're always messing around.
The world isn't the same as your ring.

83
00:05:54,033 --> 00:05:55,199
What did I do wrong?

84
00:05:55,400 --> 00:05:57,664
I was helping you and the company.

85
00:05:57,664 --> 00:05:58,299
Help me?

86
00:05:59,400 --> 00:06:01,533
Are you helping me or yourself?

87
00:06:02,766 --> 00:06:05,299
With my identity, you're causing a stir.

88
00:06:05,833 --> 00:06:07,966
Now there are three men who like you.

89
00:06:09,000 --> 00:06:09,866
Three men?

90
00:06:11,633 --> 00:06:14,266
Ling Feng, Zeng Huaishi, and...

91
00:06:17,000 --> 00:06:18,166
Lan Chen.

92
00:06:20,866 --> 00:06:21,933
Why did you come back?

93
00:06:23,466 --> 00:06:25,504
Why did you interfere with my life?

94
00:06:30,233 --> 00:06:31,166
Can you swear

95
00:06:32,233 --> 00:06:33,033
you don't like Lan Chen?

96
00:06:40,033 --> 00:06:40,866
I swear.

97
00:06:42,166 --> 00:06:43,766
If I like Lan Chen,

98
00:06:44,866 --> 00:06:46,166
I'll die in a gutter.

99
00:06:51,800 --> 00:06:53,300
What are you fighting about?

100
00:06:53,500 --> 00:06:55,104
Mom, are you feeling better?

101
00:06:55,104 --> 00:06:57,766
I'm fine. Don't worry.

102
00:06:59,633 --> 00:07:01,700
Mom, I'll get you water.

103
00:07:05,066 --> 00:07:07,000
We are a family.

104
00:07:07,133 --> 00:07:09,299
Your father always said

105
00:07:10,333 --> 00:07:13,299
we are a complete family
when we are together.

106
00:07:15,766 --> 00:07:17,599
Don't ever say you're not

107
00:07:17,866 --> 00:07:19,366
welcoming your sister back.

108
00:07:22,466 --> 00:07:23,400
It's okay, mom.

109
00:07:24,466 --> 00:07:25,366
It's all my fault.

110
00:07:27,033 --> 00:07:29,733
Whatever you do,

111
00:07:31,000 --> 00:07:31,900
I'm used to it.

112
00:07:33,233 --> 00:07:34,592
No matter what trouble,

113
00:07:35,400 --> 00:07:38,720
we must face it together.

114
00:07:39,008 --> 00:07:39,699
Understand?

115
00:07:39,699 --> 00:07:43,020
♪Engraved in my fleeting memory♪

116
00:07:43,020 --> 00:07:46,213
♪I'm immersed again♪

117
00:07:46,366 --> 00:07:48,096
Your sister is doing all for you.

118
00:07:49,033 --> 00:07:52,366
The current situation is complicated.

119
00:07:53,033 --> 00:07:57,066
Nobody can handle it better
than she does.

120
00:07:57,966 --> 00:07:58,633
But...

121
00:07:58,766 --> 00:08:02,299
Weren't you on paid leave
because you couldn't handle it?

122
00:08:07,266 --> 00:08:09,600
I'm sorry, sister.

123
00:08:09,696 --> 00:08:14,639
♪I repeatedly got lost in the scenery♪

124
00:08:17,533 --> 00:08:19,166
It's okay.

125
00:08:19,966 --> 00:08:21,533
I will handle it.

126
00:08:22,368 --> 00:08:25,664
♪Engraved in my fleeting memory♪

127
00:08:25,664 --> 00:08:29,279
♪I'm immersed again♪

128
00:08:37,366 --> 00:08:38,266
What's going on?

129
00:08:41,533 --> 00:08:43,799
Feng, they are bullying us.

130
00:08:46,066 --> 00:08:47,833
Don't be so impulsive, Bu.

131
00:08:48,466 --> 00:08:49,299
What do you want?

132
00:08:51,466 --> 00:08:53,933
We're old friends.

133
00:08:54,433 --> 00:08:56,799
I came specifically to visit you.

134
00:08:57,566 --> 00:09:01,833
First, clear the chat records on WeChat.

135
00:09:01,933 --> 00:09:03,333
Delete it.

136
00:09:03,666 --> 00:09:06,099
Then, make a short video.

137
00:09:06,533 --> 00:09:08,599
It's mainly

138
00:09:09,200 --> 00:09:11,633
about exposing Lan Chen,

139
00:09:12,000 --> 00:09:15,333
who asked you to intimidate employees.

140
00:09:15,933 --> 00:09:19,296
He's been trying

141
00:09:19,633 --> 00:09:22,133
to control the company

142
00:09:22,633 --> 00:09:23,566
by bullying.

143
00:09:24,066 --> 00:09:25,866
Simple, right?

144
00:09:26,066 --> 00:09:27,133
Would I agree?

145
00:09:27,400 --> 00:09:27,766
What's...

146
00:09:27,966 --> 00:09:29,400
Calm down, Bu.

147
00:09:29,533 --> 00:09:31,033
Don't argue with him.

148
00:09:32,033 --> 00:09:33,133
You think it over.

149
00:09:35,766 --> 00:09:38,466
Look, it's all yours.

150
00:09:38,766 --> 00:09:40,799
Do a deal. What do you say?

151
00:09:42,566 --> 00:09:43,266
Deal.

152
00:09:43,366 --> 00:09:46,300
Here you go.

153
00:09:46,933 --> 00:09:48,833
I have a scoop for you.

154
00:09:49,133 --> 00:09:49,696
What is it?

155
00:09:49,696 --> 00:09:52,033
Miss Jin has a little sister.

156
00:09:56,563 --> 00:10:01,085
♪I pass through the crowd with you♪

157
00:10:04,115 --> 00:10:09,076
♪As if we have a tacit understanding,
attracting each other♪

158
00:10:12,125 --> 00:10:17,949
♪When the loneliness cracks,
warmth seeps in♪

159
00:10:17,949 --> 00:10:25,419
♪You come with light,
shining into my heart♪

160
00:10:25,419 --> 00:10:28,900
♪Stars fall into my eyes,
and you fall into my heart♪

161
00:10:28,900 --> 00:10:33,021
♪I make a wish foolishly,
but actually, you are the shooting star♪

162
00:10:33,021 --> 00:10:34,717
♪Open my secret♪

163
00:10:34,717 --> 00:10:40,765
♪I hope you find
all the tenderness hidden for you♪

164
00:10:40,765 --> 00:10:44,637
♪Sinking into your love,
I want to sink deeper♪

165
00:10:44,637 --> 00:10:49,143
♪With each breath,
I can feel the sweetness♪

166
00:10:49,143 --> 00:10:57,853
♪Two lonely islands meet,
and it's the gift of fate♪
